    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>No difference at all. According to \n<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jls/se7/html/jls-8.html#jls-8.3.1\" rel=\"noreferrer\">8.3.1 - Classes - Field Modifiers of the Java Language Specification</a>,</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>If two or more (distinct) field modifiers appear in a field declaration, it is customary, though not required, that they appear in the order consistent with that shown above in the production for FieldModifier.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>For fields, the said production lists the modifiers in this order:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p><code>@Annotation</code> <code>public</code> <code>protected</code> <code>private</code> <code>static</code> <code>final</code> <code>transient</code> <code>volatile</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>And for methods:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p><code>@Annotation</code> <code>public</code> <code>protected</code> <code>private</code> <code>abstract</code> <code>static</code> <code>final</code> <code>synchronized</code> <code>native</code> <code>strictfp</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 47283,
      "reputation" : 723399,
      "user_id" : 139985,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 69,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/147c5a9cc1feec049c50da791ac7d144?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Stephen C",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/139985/stephen-c"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 59,
    "last_activity_date" : 1340772634,
    "creation_date" : 1340772634,
    "answer_id" : 11219601,
    "question_id" : 11219556,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>They are the same.  The order of modifiers is not significant.  And note that the same rule applies in <em>all</em> contexts where modifiers are used in Java.</p>\n\n<p>However, most Java style guides recommend/mandate the same specific order for the modifiers. In this case, it is <code>public static final</code>.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 269622,
      "reputation" : 59807,
      "user_id" : 559070,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 74,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/58cd4a26cf2d5bcd36c125fe8cc8464b?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Harry Joy",
