    "answer_id" : 11219628,
    "question_id" : 11219556,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<blockquote>\n  <p>What is the difference between them or are they same?</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>If you are talking about changing order of static and final then yes they are same.</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>does it differ for private or public?</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>No, you can use any order in private and public. Just difference is private variables will not be accessible outside of class directly.</p>\n"
  }, {
